summary: An ordinance accepting a deed dated December 30, 1910, from School District \#1, a municipal corporation, to the City of Seattle, a municipal corporation, to lots 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 and 8, lots 25, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 31, 32, in block 3, Parker's Addition to the City of Seattle, in accordance with the Board of Park Commissioners, the 24th day of October, 1910, and ordinance of the City Council No. 25798, given in exchange for property in block 2, Parker's Addition, and transferred to the Board of Park Commissioners.
